WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.028
Anything you send digitally can be screenshotted, forwarded, or saved.

00:00:03.078 --> 00:00:06.106
There is no truly private message. Before you hit send, ask — would

00:00:06.156 --> 00:00:09.184
I be okay with my manager or the customer's spouse reading this exact

00:00:09.234 --> 00:00:12.262
text?
